# ee641350ef204e7991f90217bd566d0a
#: ../../appendices/faq.en.rst:387
msgid ""
"If the Traffic Server ``bin`` directory is not in your path, then prepend"
" the Traffic Line commands with ``./`` (for example, ``./traffic_ctl "
"-h``)."
